@host = https://localhost:1339
# 1337 is gateway, 1338 is software api, 1339 is vendors api.
### Adding a Vendor

POST {{host}}/vendors HTTP/1.1
Host: software-api
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"Hypertheory","url":"https://www.jetbrains.com",
"pointOfContact":{"name":"Shirley","email":"shirley@jetbrains.com","phone":"555-1212"}}


### Change Point of Contact

PUT {{host}}/vendors/bcda1cd9-09fb-44dd-bd92-ace8de8d51b0/point-of-contact HTTP/1.1
Host: software-api
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"adam","email":"satya@microsoft.com","phone":"555-1212"}


### GET all vendors

GET {{host}}/vendors


### Get individual vendor

GET {{host}}/vendors/bcda1cd9-09fb-44dd-bd92-ace8de8d51b0